bboxParam.description:
Stations within a given bounding box (in WGS84 by default). Refer to the crs parameter if a  non-default CRS shall be used.

```json  bbox={
  "ll": {
    "type": "Point",
    "coordinates": [<x>,<y>]
  },
  "ur": {
    "type": "Point",
    "coordinates": [<x>,<y>]
  }
}
```

nearParam.description:
Stations within a given bounding box (in WGS84 by default). Refer to the `crs` parameter if a  non-default CRS shall be used.

```json near={
  "center": {
    "type": "Point",
    "coordinates": [<x>,<y>]
  },
  "radius":500
}
```
